PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Supply and Services of PETER A.G. CAMERON, of Toronto, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Post Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of six months; and approval that PETER A.G. CAMERON act as Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Canada Post Corporation for a term of six months, effective September 12, 1995.
